        <mxCell id="m1-body" value="Every PR reviewed against project standards.&#xa;&#xa;Scored on 0–10 rubric. PRs below threshold auto-rejected with specific comments.&#xa;&#xa;Standards are enforced at commit time, not during review meetings." style="text;html=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;fontSize=11;fontColor=#334155;" vertex="1" parent="1">
